Attribution of sources

This book collects and contrasts English terminology (primarily from
K. Rosen, "Discrete Mathematics and Its Applications") with Vietnamese
terminology drawn from cited Vietnamese sources. Each Vietnamese term is
accompanied by a citation to its source. All cited works remain the property of
their respective copyright holders; citations are used for scholarly reference
and identification only.
